Well done ChattChitto, another brilliant release.
I had TuneUp 2011 already, but when it updated my (less-than-legal) serial was rejected.

I had massive problems getting it to work with this installer so after much persistance, this is what you must do:

1. Open task manager and close all instances of TuneUp you find
2. Uninstall TuneUp
3. Reboot (absolutely necessary)
4. Go to the AppData folder in the documents folder.
5. Delete all instances of TuneUp in both Local and Roaming folders
6. (I recommend you turn off your internet connection here)
7. Use ChattChitto's installer (if you don't want to turn off your installer, check custom installation and make sure you deselect update upon installation)
8. When installation finished, use task manager to again kill all instances of TuneUp
9. Use ChattChitto's automated crack
10. Run TuneUp
11. When it shouts at you that it is not a valid copy, DON'T PANIC, enter ChattChitto's serial (any)
12. It should work. If not, you either did something wrong or you are well and truly screwed.
